  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Card
    This is the main class for the card.
    CardTest
    This is a test class for testing the methods in the Card class.
    CardTypeTest
    This is a test class for testing CardType enum.
    Continent
    This class defines properties for a continent like name of continent, controls values and list of the countries.
    ContinentTest
    This is a test class for testing the methods in the Continent class.
    Country
    This class defines properties of country like its coordinates, the continent to which country belongs, its adjacent countries, and whether it's been assigned to any player or not.
    CountryTest
    This is a test class for testing the methods in the Country class.
    EntityTestSuite
    This is a Test suite Class for all classes in Entity package.
    Hmap
    This class describes Map and its list of continents.
    HmapTest
    This is a test class for testing the methods in the Hmap class.
    Player
    This class defines Player with its properties like id, name, armies and number of countries won by player.
    PlayerTest
    This is a test class for testing the methods in the Player class.
